## ðŸ§ª `Install.ps1` â€“ One-Click Installer

> This downloads and installs the module from a remote ZIP.

```powershell
# Install.ps1
param(
    [string]$DownloadUrl = "https://yourdomain.com/PHWhatsapp.zip"
)

$moduleName = "PHWhatsapp"
$installPath = "C:\Program Files\WindowsPowerShell\Modules\$moduleName"
$zipFile = "$env:TEMP\$moduleName.zip"

Write-Host "Downloading PHWhatsapp module from $DownloadUrl..."
Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $DownloadUrl -OutFile $zipFile -UseBasicParsing

Write-Host "Extracting to $installPath..."
Expand-Archive -Path $zipFile -DestinationPath $installPath -Force

Remove-Item $zipFile -Force

Import-Module $moduleName -Force
Write-Host "PHWhatsapp module installed and loaded successfully."

Write-Host "`nSet credentials like this:"
Write-Host "Set-WhatsappConfig -IdInstance 'YOUR_ID' -ApiToken 'YOUR_TOKEN'"
